{"tid":540270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【青永屍墳場新聞】曹仁超專訪：我無本事讀浸會","createTime":"2018-01-25T10:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T12:26:33.000Z","uid":35221,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2b43266cf6751ac68ce5273d9f891bb4666bdca9","tid":540270,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/cemeterynews.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/59B3CF4A-E626-49C3-9BCF-F3D3E1D76C5C.gif?zoom=1.25&amp;fit=400%2C267\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fcemeterynews.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F59B3CF4A-E626-49C3-9BCF-F3D3E1D76C5C.gif%3Fzoom%3D1.25%26fit%3D400%252C267&h=02cb42fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曹仁超專訪：我無本事讀浸會<br />\nPOSTED ON 01/25/2018 BY 墳場新聞總編輯 <br />\n<br />\n[特稿]<br />\n恆指升勢凌厲，編輯局約見財經專欄作家曹仁超（1948-2016），商談如何拓展陽間業務。<br />\n<br />\n曹仁超直接表示：「你們總編輯貧窮，並不是因為沉迷女色或日色，而是勢的問題。現在恆指不斷升、不斷升，是因為恆指成份股轉換了，所以才升，你們總編輯聽到成份股變動時都不懂得買港交所，而居然去買他鍾情的男歌手唱片，這是十分笨的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/cemeterynews.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/F93E9313-084F-40C2-9ADD-93B295E516C8.jpeg?w=322\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fcemeterynews.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2FF93E9313-084F-40C2-9ADD-93B295E516C8.jpeg%3Fw%3D322&h=c6dd45f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曹仁超當頭棒喝，編輯部十分感激，並表示可以幫曹先生報讀浸會大學的經濟系，以作報答，使曹先生可以在死後考取學位。<br />\n<br />\n但曹仁超婉拒，指：「這所大學畢業前要考普通話，我的普通話雖然在大江南北通行，人人都能聽懂，但我猜他們這種模糊的考綱編成的考試，我是考不上的，我又不能裝是新移民，無謂浪費學費和你們的苦心。」<br />\n<br />\n曹仁超寄語總編輯，早日止蝕，不宜過度投資。<br />\n<br />\n轉自Cemetery News 墳場新聞網頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://cemeterynews.org/2018/01/25/cho_chi_ming/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcemeterynews.org%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2Fcho_chi_ming%2F&d=eV%2BAlnDYlvQ81GvqFlsP%2BACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=54be814a\" target=\"_blank\">http://cemeterynews.org/2018/01/25/cho_chi_ming/</a>"},{"pid":"d28873011879430008be38720035f423e8444d5e","tid":540270,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:45:11.000Z","msg":"大師我明你個C係向上架ma <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2ad15bb29f350047bfc618b94a5fc0cb8843dc","tid":540270,"uid":34223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T11:16:05.000Z","msg":"墳場新聞啲野幾好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前劉璋臨時造勢大會果篇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61894fa11ee6899b7de9dbc112ba7f1ba84833c5","tid":540270,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:14:33.000Z","msg":"淨係識寫埋啲濕鳩廢文，對香港大局有咩幫助？做佢嘅老師把啦憤總。"},{"pid":"3fbee4f4c81bfd8d0c6d9a9564e6c725575dc60e","tid":540270,"uid":137731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:25:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f2ca883f8e246554d0f6836dde1de5f9434d5a3","tid":540270,"uid":34852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}